{"tid":2009163,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方譴責他人於510到各商場破壞社會安寧，警方定會果斷執法！！","createTime":"2020-05-09T14:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T04:34:43.000Z","uid":219007,"like":108,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"862d60f8bbccc219a7e84b590da1e0c11e6db1fe","tid":2009163,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:08:54.000Z","msg":"【 警方譴責網民煽動他人在母親節期間到各商場破壞社會安寧 】<br />\n<br />\n警方發現有網民號召於母親節期間，在全港多個商場以快閃的方式集結並煽動他人做出破壞社會安寧的行爲。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴厲譴責煽動他人破壞社會安寧的行為。母親節乃普天同慶的日子，正當市民享受天倫之樂，不法分子竟然利用不同藉口煽動他人爲非作歹，破壞節日氣氛及危害公衆安全，令人氣憤。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據香港法例第599G章《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》，於五月八日至五月二十一日期間，不得在任何公眾地方進行多於8人的羣組聚集。任何人士參與或組織受禁羣組聚集均屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n市民切勿以身試法，警方定會果斷執法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/3164024883685454/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F960526577368640%2Fposts%2F3164024883685454%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=4b4ca7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/3164024883685454/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9498f44a30c039de4574220a7eaf00906a68dd","tid":2009163,"uid":247032,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"行街唱歌咋喎！<br />\n又唔係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賣白粉</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed01e9ad77a804dda29bb3560d86a1df4f1f2d72","tid":2009163,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class